{"word":"H6536 - פָּרַס - pâraç - paw-ras' - Deal","slug":"H6536","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">פָּרַס</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pâraç"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>paw-ras'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Deal"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05E8;&#x05E1; - pa&#x0302;ras</b> - <i>paw-ras'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>break</i> in pieces, that is, (usually without violence) to <i>split</i>, <i>distribute: - </i>deal, divide, have hoofs, part, tear."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6538\">H6538</a>, <a href=\"#/H6541\">H6541</a>"}]}